imdb.plot outline: Professional photographer and lighting expert Bob Davis walks you through using "dirty lighting" (the mixing of various light sources and temperatures) to create fun lighting set-ups and unique results. This unique video training offering shows you how you can get quality photographic lighting results with flashlights, spotlights, and daylight fluorescents, all on a budget of $100 or less.
